title: THE SALON: New Years Eve Eve 2015
desc: Some say New Year's Eve is amateur night; that's 'cause all the dames and dapper gents know the real party is the night ? before - at THE SALON - what we like to call NEW YEAR's EVE EVE.? For our 8th annual NYEE extravaganza we return to a favorite venue, THE DL, and continue the tradition with a ? spectacular lineup of over 50 performers, including 6 bands, on three floors for your lounging and groovin' pleasure! ? NYEE is our biggest party of the year, so advance tickets are strongly recommended! more info at? http://www.thesalon.biz
